<br>
<br>
AS OF APRIL 4th THESE CLASSES ARE TEMPORARILY CLOSED<br>
DRUIDS, MONKS, SHAMANS, RANGERS<br>
<br>
<br>
If for some reason you do not meet the requirements and still feel like you would be an asset to ODY send me a tell in game.<br>
I am DREAMSTALKER!!!!!!! We will discuss it.<br>
Thank you for your interest in Odysseys.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
1: Our Minimum Requirements:<br>
<br>
Level: 65*<br>
Equipment:<br>
Permanent EB item<br>
At least 1 insta clicky item (usable indoor/outdoor)<br>
Resist gears 120 in ALL RESISTS!!!<br>
Keys - PoV/PoS abled, normal old world keys, at least 2 pieces of emperor key and 3 shards for VT key!!!<br>
AA skills- ALL MUST HAVE run 3 <br>
<br>
<br>
IF YOU ALREADY APPLIED YOU ARE IN UNDER THE GRANDFATHER LAW!!!!<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
2: Loot Policy:<br>
<br>
Odysseys was founded on a merit loot system, and remains so to this day. As an applicant you have accrued no merit. Once you have attained Trial status you will become eligible for –some- no-drop items. <br>
<br>
<br>
3: Play time:<br>
<br>
LOTS – We are a US-based RAID Guild. We are looking for players that are able to play 6-12pm PST or EST (either time zone applies). Attendance to guild raids will be a large influence to your acceptance into the guild. <br>
<br>
<br>
4: Application Initiation:<br>
<br>
You need you to state in your posted** application:<br>
Who you are. (Class, Level)<br>
How many AA's you have.<br>
Your alts and their levels.<br>
Do you have your epic?<br>
Your raid experience - planes, dragons, etc.<br>
What is you prior guild history.<br>
Your goals in Odysseys, and what can you do for Odysseys.<br>
Your regular playing hours.<br>
<br>
That was the easy part….<br>
<br>
<br>
5: How do i become an REAL MEMBER:<br>
Attend 5 REAL raids(real raid is a raid that involves 80% or more of the guild) and you become a trial member.<br>
After becoming a trial you have 30 days to prove yourself to other guild members, because at this time you will be up for a vote by all REGULAR members (You need 80% of the guild to vote yes) If you pass you become a real member of Ody.<br>
<br>
<br>
6: There is no Rule #6<br>
<br>
<br>
7: How will people know me?<br>
<br>
<br>
1) Raid attendance<br>
2) Focusing on the task at hand during the raids<br>
3) Group with our members outside of raids<br>
4) Assist in spotting mobs for the guild to raid (additional faction building)<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
8: You made it past the vote!!!<br>
<br>
Congratulations in becoming a member of the best guild on Xev! <br>
<br>
<br>
*Before you post your application please make sure you visit our web site and review or policies. <br>
<br>
**Your ezboard name must be the same as your mains name.<br>
